=====Usage notes=====
* {{lang|zh|勺}} was adopted as the standard simplification of {{zh-l|杓|sháo}} in the {{w|second round of simplified Chinese characters}}. The current standard, the ''{{w|Table of General Standard Chinese Characters}}'', includes {{lang|zh|杓}}, but it is intended to only be used for the ''biāo'' reading according to ''Tongyong Guifan Hanzi Zidian''. Dictionaries from Mainland China, such as ''{{w|Xiandai Hanyu Cidian}}'' and ''{{w|Xiandai Hanyu Guifan Cidian}}'', treat {{lang|zh|杓}} as an alternative form of {{zh-l|勺}}.

